description: The United States is close to a decision on providing Ukraine with ATACMs, which are guided missiles with a range of up to 300 kilometers (about 186 miles), a top aide to President Volodymyr Zelensky said Friday.
title: July 14, 2023 - Russia-Ukraine news

author: Mohammed Tawfeeq
description: The United States, France and the United Kingdom have condemned Russia’s move to block the proposed extension of a United Nations’ cross-border operation that delivers aid to millions of people in Syria from Turkey.
title: Syria aid: Russia slammed as 'inhumane' after blocking UN cross-border aid operation | CNN

author: By Joshua Berlinger, Thom Poole, Adrienne Vogt and Matt Meyer, CNN
description: Ukraine says it is slowly grinding forward on the southern and eastern front lines as Russian forces throw "everything they can" at slowing down the counteroffensive.
title: July 15, 2023 Russia-Ukraine war news

author: Barbie Latza Nadeau
description: The case of Emanuela Orlandi, the 15-year-old daughter of a Vatican employee who went missing in Rome 40 years ago, has taken another twist as her brother dismissed what he described as a “shameful” attempt by the Vatican and Rome prosecutors to cast blame on the family by suggesting a dead uncle was behind the teenager’s unsolved disappearance.
title: Another twist in the 40-year-old missing 'Vatican girl' case | CNN

author: Jacob Lev
description: An emotional Damar Hamlin presented the Pat Tillman Award for Service at the 2023 ESPYS to the Buffalo Bills training staff who helped save his life during a game earlier this year.
title: Damar Hamlin is overcome with emotion at ESPY Awards while presenting service award to Buffalo Bills training staff | CNN

author: Sharon Braithwaite,Josh Pennington
description: Kosovo President Vjosa Osmani and Albania’s Prime Minister Edi Rama condemned the brawl that erupted Thursday in the Kosovo parliament between opposition and ruling party MPs.
title: Kosovo president condemns brawl that erupted in parliament | CNN

author: Radina Gigova,Svitlana Vlasova
description: Amid the raging war and constant threat of Russian missiles, a successful heart transplant has been performed on a 6-year-old girl in Kyiv, authorities with the Heart Institute of Ukraine’s Ministry of Health announced on Monday.
title: Girl receives heart of 4-year-old-boy in first transplant of its kind in Ukraine, despite raging war | CNN

author: Matt Foster
description: Former Manchester City footballer Benjamin Mendy has asked for privacy to begin “rebuilding his life” after he was found not guilty on a charge of rape and a separate charge of attempted rape.
title:
Former Manchester City footballer Benjamin Mendy found not guilty of rape and attempted rape
Benjamin Mendy: Former Manchester City footballer found not guilty of rape and attempted rape | CNN

author: Homero De la Fuente
description: Phoenix Mercury superstar Brittney Griner marked a successful return to the WNBA All-Star Game on Saturday, her first since being released from a Russian penal colony last December.
title: Brittney Griner makes triumphant return in her first WNBA All-Star Game since Russian detention | CNN

author: Andrew Carey,Yulia Kesaieva
description: Despite an underwhelming first month of Ukraine’s much-anticipated summer push to liberate territory from Russian forces, Kyiv says its Western backers are not pressuring the country for quick results.
title: Ukraine's counteroffensive grinds on, but western allies remain patient, Kyiv says | CNN

author: Wayne Sterling
description: Argentine superstar Lionel Messi is reportedly expected to make his Inter Miami debut on July 21, club managing owner Jorge Mas told a small group of reporters Monday, according to the Miami Herald.
title: Lionel Messi reportedly expected to make Inter Miami debut in July | CNN

description: Ukraine says it is slowly grinding forward on the southern and eastern front lines as Russian forces throw "everything they can" at slowing down the counteroffensive. Follow live updates.
title: Live updates: Russia's war in Ukraine

description: NBA superstar LeBron James will switch back to jersey number 23 for the Los Angeles Lakers’ upcoming season, the team announced on Saturday.
title: LeBron James will switch back to jersey number 23 'out of respect' for the late Bill Russell | CNN

description: A crucial deal allowing the export of grain from Ukraine is set to expire Monday unless Russia agrees to an extension.
title: Crucial grain deal set on the brink of expiring | CNN

description: Russia has a stockpile of cluster munitions and will consider using them against Ukraine “if they are used against us,” President Vladimir Putin said.
title: Putin says Russia has 'sufficient' cluster munitions and may retaliate if Ukraine uses them | CNN
